Andate, ma fate piano.

404
00:30:22,765 --> 00:30:23,765
[Angelica] Grazie.

405
00:30:25,085 --> 00:30:25,925
[uomo] Annamo.

406
00:30:26,805 --> 00:30:29,325
[Alex sospira]

407
00:30:45,485 --> 00:30:47,725
Mo hai capito chi cazzo comanda, sì?

408
00:31:09,245 --> 00:31:11,965
